# Translate README.md

## Overview

Translate README.md in specified directory or in the same directory of specified file on current tab.

## Requirement
When user types "/trans-readme":
1. Read the README.md file in the current directory
2. Translate the Vietnamese content to English and save as README.en.md
3. Translate the Vietnamese content to Japanese and save as README.ja.md
4. Ensure all files have language navigation links at the top:
   `[English](README.en.md) - [日本語](README.ja.md) - [Tiếng Việt](README.md)`
5. Maintain the same structure and formatting
6. Update relative links to point to correct language versions

## Translation Guidelines
- Keep technical terms in English (bookmarklet, JavaScript, etc.)
- Preserve code blocks and examples exactly
- Update navigation links to appropriate language versions
- Maintain markdown formatting and structure
- For UI elements, use standard translations (Chrome: "Bookmark Manager" -> "ブックマークマネージャー")
